snippet.title: Project Lambda (UE4)
snippet.description:
Hello. 
There were many questions about the status of the project.
The project is now frozen indefinitely.
Download Link: https://cloud.mail.ru/public/mfdX/WQueFXcg3 (Left at the top of the arrow icon. In the dropping menu, put a tick in a square and press the blue button)
